<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-18 00:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5342 &Cx1f; tad-z
b a BC-CVN-MAIN18-1STLD-COX     08-18 1464
