<P>
   &QL; 
 &UR; BRIGHT IDEAS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   _ In order to take advantage of the youthful passion for rainbow
hair colors, Clairol has a new XtremeFX hair color line aimed at
13- to 24-year-olds. Product manager  &UR; Karen Murabito &LR;  told the Wall
Street Journal that the company had rewritten its standard
instructions, using new ones with graffiti-style drawings and
phrases such as ``get it on'' instead of ``apply the product.''
