<HEADLINE>
KURSK DEBACLE EXPOSES RUSSIA'S BROADER MILITARY WEAKNESS  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors...NOTE 125-word trim; 900 uncut)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 900-word material from The New York
