<P>
   REL-LOTZ _ Anne Graham Lotz, 51, the daughter of evangelist
Billy Graham, has taken to the road in recent months, spreading the
word of God as part of a conference called, ``Just Give Me Jesus.''
The conference _ it comes to Atlanta next week _ is hugely
successful, drawing tens of thousands of women at each stop. Lotz
says she is driven by a personal need to be closer to God and to
reach others even as some Baptist evangelicals turn their backs on
her. (White, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   HISPANICS _ Austin's seminaries are making a concentrated effort
to offer Hispanics theological education. Together, they are
starting an institute with a grant. Meanwhile, next week Austin
Presby Seminary also opens a Hispanic theological institute that
has moved from Atlanta into the seminary here. (Perkes, Austin
American-Statesman). 15.
</P>
