<P>
   THE WEEKEND DUTY EDITORS ARE:
</P>
<P>
   IN ATLANTA: Diane Fall at 404-526-5456
</P>
<P>
   IN WASHINGTON: Rick Christie at 301-809-3419; 301-910-6248
(cellular).
