<P>
   COXNET HEALTHY LIVING0819 _ With New Year's Day verve, countless
people resolved to eat healthy foods. Those promises are long
forgotten by many, and it's back to life in the fast-food lane. But
summer's the perfect time to recommit _ seasonal produce offers
vitality in juicy, fleshy flavors. (Walker, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
