harvest _ deliver the maximum nutritional value. But fresh produce
</P>
<P>
   that has been stored incorrectly or for too long will have less
nutritional punch than frozen vegetables.
</P>
<P>
   How do you measure how healthy your community is? A new Web
site, the federally funded Community Health Status Indicators
Project (www.communityhealth.hrsa.govcq majm), can answer that
question. (McKenna, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
