<P>
   EBAY-POWERSELLERS (Undated) _ The real powers behind eBay's
success are those small operators _ the liquidators, wholesalers,
small retail shops and stay-at-home entrepreneurs _ that offer the
bulk of goods for sale on the eBay site. Call them power sellers _
eBay does. By Lisa Guernsey.
</P>
