   With graphic.
</P>
<P>
   EBAY-CONSUMERS (Undated) _ A consumer with a complaint against
an eBay ``power seller'' says that when push comes to shove, eBay
isn't prepared to follow through on consumer-protection promises.
By Barbara Whitaker.
</P>
<P>
   BERNSTEIN-ALLIANCE (Undated) _ With analysts' research
increasingly suspect, connected as it is to their firms
investment-banking business, Sanford Bernstein's research
operations stand out for their independence. But will that last,
now that Bernstein is being bought by Alliance Capital? By Alex
Berenson
</P>
